03:07.330 --> 03:10.250
<b>Imperial Relic Black Marlin!</b>

03:11.250 --> 03:16.920
<b>Created from an organ of an aquatic Danger Beast that controls water,</b>

03:16.920 --> 03:21.130
<b>this Relic allows its wielder to freely manipulate any liquid within range.</b>

03:21.930 --> 03:26.510
<b>That I should face you two in such a location is fortunate indeed.</b>

03:28.730 --> 03:30.850
<b>A water-controller, huh?</b>

03:30.850 --> 03:33.230
<b>How appropriate for the servant of one who controls ice.</b>

03:33.770 --> 03:37.320
<b>Lady Esdeath can create ice from nothing.</b>

03:37.320 --> 03:39.190
<b>She is on a completely different level.</b>

03:39.190 --> 03:41.240
<b>It's awe-inspiring!</b>

03:41.240 --> 03:42.280
<b>Water Spirit Cannon!</b>

03:43.660 --> 03:44.950
<b>How brazen!</b>

03:47.910 --> 03:49.830
<b>Ow, ow, ow...</b>

03:49.830 --> 03:53.040
<b>That armored guy is second only to Lady Esdeath in strength.</b>

03:53.460 --> 03:56.500
<b>But with all this water around, 
Liver can defeat him.</b>

03:56.960 --> 03:58.210
<b>I should back him up.</b>

03:58.210 --> 03:59.420
<b>Hold it!</b>

04:02.630 --> 04:06.300
<b>I'm not gonna hide behind him the whole time!</b>

04:06.600 --> 04:08.220
<b>This guy...</b>

04:08.220 --> 04:09.770
<b>Butt out!</b>

04:10.730 --> 04:12.060
<b>Night Raid...</b>

04:12.060 --> 04:13.480
<b>You're getting cocky!</b>

04:31.500 --> 04:34.080
<b><i>Damn! He's ridiculously fast!</i></b>

04:37.000 --> 04:37.790
<b><i>However...</i></b>

04:44.340 --> 04:46.010
<b>Akame is faster!</b>

04:46.300 --> 04:48.850
<b>Hmph! Don't compare me to some assassin!</b>

04:56.100 --> 04:59.770
<b><i>If I wasn't wounded already, 
this guy would be nothing.</i></b>

05:00.230 --> 05:03.950
<b><i>He's absurdly fast, given the condition he's in.</i></b>

05:03.950 --> 05:05.320
<b><i>The Three Beasts...</i></b>

05:05.320 --> 05:08.490
<b><i>Ogre was a pushover compared to these guys.</i></b>

05:20.040 --> 05:23.300
<b>Whoa, he's not messing around.</b>

05:24.130 --> 05:27.390
<b>As long as there's water around, Liver has the advantage!</b>

05:27.390 --> 05:30.810
<b>Yeah, right. Bro has this in the bag.</b>

05:30.810 --> 05:32.060
<b>Liver's gonna win!</b>

05:32.060 --> 05:33.310
<b>No, Bro's gonna win!</b>

05:33.310 --> 05:36.980
<b>Prepare to be crushed, Bulat!</b>

05:41.110 --> 05:42.860
<b>Ravine Serpent!</b>

05:58.250 --> 06:01.840
<b>I figured you'd attack the serpent head-on instead of dodging it,</b>

06:02.340 --> 06:05.880
<b>given the casualties it'd cause if it hit the boat.</b>

06:06.340 --> 06:11.970
<b>However, now that you're off the deck and in the air,</b>

06:11.970 --> 06:13.930
<b>there's no way you can dodge this!{how can he be airborne for the duration of an entire explanatory monologue}</b>

06:16.310 --> 06:17.980
<b>Dark Dragon Spear!</b>

06:26.360 --> 06:28.320
<b>A splash of water here and there</b>

06:28.320 --> 06:30.450
<b>isn't enough to quench my resolve!</b>

06:32.070 --> 06:33.200
<b>Indeed.</b>

06:33.200 --> 06:36.410
<b>That attack was hardly enough to defeat you.</b>

06:38.330 --> 06:40.460
<b>I am well aware of that.</b>

06:41.170 --> 06:44.670
<b>We have survived countless battles together.</b>

06:44.670 --> 06:49.590
<b>I understand your strength and your determination better than anyone.</b>

06:49.970 --> 06:52.050
<b>And that's precisely why...</b>

06:52.050 --> 06:56.470
<b>I'll have you taste my greatest technique!</b>

06:57.140 --> 06:59.140
<b>Water Dragon's Divine Conquest! {>screaming in high pressure water}</b>

07:14.160 --> 07:15.330
<b>Did I get him?</b>

07:16.950 --> 07:20.160
<b>If you have to ask yourself that question,</b>

07:20.160 --> 07:22.670
<b>the answer is always no!{lol}</b>

07:22.670 --> 07:24.000
<b>He survived it!</b>

07:35.930 --> 07:37.850
<b>Too bad.</b>

07:37.850 --> 07:40.640
<b>You missed your chance to take Liver out.</b>

07:42.850 --> 07:44.270
<b>Bro...</b>

07:45.270 --> 07:46.360
<b>Tatsumi?</b>

07:46.360 --> 07:48.900
<b>Forgive me, Bro.</b>

07:49.570 --> 07:53.200
<b>I wasn't able to hold him off long enough.{useless bitch}</b>

07:53.530 --> 07:54.570
<b>What's this?</b>

07:54.570 --> 07:56.330
<b>You can still move?</b>

07:56.950 --> 08:01.330
<b>I told you I'd play with you later if you kept still like a good boy.</b>

08:01.330 --> 08:02.960
<b>Don't worry about it.</b>

08:06.040 --> 08:09.300
<b>Surviving as long as you have 
with no Relic is impressive enough.{ah but doesn't having a relic make it easier to die}</b>

08:09.760 --> 08:10.800
<b>Bro...</b>

08:11.630 --> 08:14.260
<b><i>Even with all that armor, 
he's pretty badly wounded.</i></b>

08:14.640 --> 08:19.770
<b>Looks like your Relic deactivates 
when it receives enough damage.</b>

08:20.470 --> 08:21.930
<b>It's clear who's come out on top.</b>

08:23.230 --> 08:25.150
<b>I wouldn't call the match just yet.</b>

