19:32.810 --> 19:35.820
<b>If you're this powerful already,</b>

19:35.820 --> 19:37.900
<b>I'm sure that one day</b>

19:37.900 --> 19:40.740
<b>you will surpass me.</b>

19:44.160 --> 19:46.330
<b><i>Keep moving forward.</i></b>

19:47.040 --> 19:49.370
<b><i>I'll be watching over you.</i></b>

